Program: Discovery
Title: Scarring
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxvt
Last Broadcast Date: 06 June 2001
How our understanding of wound healing has been transformed. Until recently the mechanisms that lie just below our skin and helped us heal were a mystery. Scientists now believe they now know more about the body's fightback after a serious wound, knowledge that could help patients with serious trauma injuries. Show less